.sp
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.PP
This function stores the OpenSC cache directory for the current user in the buffer pointed to by
\fIbuf\fR, which is
\fIbufsize\fR
bytes long\&.
.SH "RETURN VALUE"
.PP
Returns 0 if successful, or a negative value in case of error\&.
